      "span_text": "As the use of cinchonidine had been reported by Loh and co-workers as a suitable chiral auxiliary for the asymmetric addition of allylindium reagents to aldehydes, we set to investigate the effect of cinchonidine on the allylation of benzaldehyde in Table 1 ), and a neglectable ee was observed (entry 1, Table 5 )."
